      "text": "And in that house, one night a Ukrainian boy discovered voices and went running to the Germans and said, there are Jews hiding there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Jews-- the German police came, a whole 20 or 50 of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they dug a small hole and they said to the Jews, we know you are there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You either come out or we burn you alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
